title: Who

description.plain:
On July 18, 2024) it was announced to be focus track from Jimin’s second studio album, Muse. Released on July 19 2024.
The song and the whole album was recorded before he went to the military. It was recorded before the filming of Are You Sure?
Written by GHSTLOOP, Tenroc, Pdogg, Jon Bellion & Pete Nappi and produced by  Jon Bellion, Pete Nappi, Tenroc, Pdogg & GHSTLOOP.
Debuted at number 14 on the Billboard Hot 100
